WEBVTT

00:03.404 --> 00:06.107
PREPARING FOR HER FIRST MEET
WITH THE DEBATE TEAM.

00:06.107 --> 00:09.377
WHAT?
SHE MADE THE DEBATE TEAM?
UH-HUH.

00:09.377 --> 00:11.279
DID THEY NEED A CRIER?

00:13.714 --> 00:16.283
[ Imitating crying ]
TESTING MAKEUP ON ANIMALS

00:16.283 --> 00:18.386
SHOULD BE OUTLAWED...

00:20.788 --> 00:22.656
...BECAUSE BUNNIES
ARE CUTE.

00:23.791 --> 00:25.626
IT BURNS THEIR EYES.

00:25.626 --> 00:28.796
AND THEN THEY'RE BLIND,
AND THEY HOP INTO TRAFFIC.

00:30.331 --> 00:34.068
SEE, MY MASCARA'S RUNNING!
THEY DIED FOR NOTHING!

00:34.068 --> 00:36.270
Carmen: WELL...

00:36.270 --> 00:39.473
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF MY DEBATE OUTFIT?

00:39.473 --> 00:41.575
CARMEN, ARE YOU
DRESSING LIKE THAT

00:41.575 --> 00:44.545
'CAUSE YOUR EX-BOYFRIEND'S
ON THE OPPOSING TEAM?

00:44.545 --> 00:45.779
YEP.

00:45.779 --> 00:48.349
NO ONE CHEATS ON ME
WITHOUT PAYING THE PRICE.

00:48.349 --> 00:50.951
I'M GONNA DISTRACT JASON
WITH MY BODY

00:50.951 --> 00:54.088
AND DESTROY HIM
WITH MY MIND.

00:54.088 --> 00:59.427
"HELL HATH NO FURY
LIKE A WOMAN SCORNED."

01:01.262 --> 01:05.099
I'VE DISTRACTED
WITH MY BODY.

01:05.099 --> 01:08.469
I'VE DESTROYED
WITH MY BODY.

01:08.469 --> 01:11.239
I REMEMBER A TIME
WHEN I DISTRACTED ONE GUY

01:11.239 --> 01:13.807
WHILE I DESTROYED
THE OTHER.

01:19.147 --> 01:20.648
I REMEMBER THAT DAY.

01:20.648 --> 01:23.917
YOU FORGOT TO PUT A SOCK
ON THE FRONT DOOR,

01:23.917 --> 01:26.620
AND I WALKED IN ON YOU.

01:26.620 --> 01:30.458
THAT WAS NOT
A GOOD MOTHER'S DAY FOR ME.

01:30.458 --> 01:32.326
CAN YOU
HELP HER PRACTICE?

01:32.326 --> 01:34.262
HERE ARE
THE EVIDENCE CARDS.

01:34.262 --> 01:36.130
I GOT TO GO
MEET A CLIENT.

01:36.130 --> 01:39.733
OKAY, DAD,
YOU'RE ARGUING FOR SUVs,

01:39.733 --> 01:41.369
AND I'M MAKING A CASE
FOR HYBRID CARS.

01:41.369 --> 01:42.903
OKAY, GOOD LUCK.

01:42.903 --> 01:44.672
[ SIGHS ]
RESOLVED --

01:44.672 --> 01:47.408
SUVs GUZZLE GAS
AND DESTROY THE ENVIRONMENT

01:47.408 --> 01:50.844
AND KEEP US AT THE MERCY
OF OIL-RICH FOREIGN GOVERNMENTS.

01:50.844 --> 01:55.316
MAYBE, BUT MY SUV's
GOT A LEATHER INTERIOR,

01:55.316 --> 01:56.750
A SIX-CD CHANGER,

01:56.750 --> 01:59.953
AND HYBRIDS BOUNCE OFF ME
LIKE BULLETS OFF SUPERMAN!

01:59.953 --> 02:01.989
WA-CHA!

02:01.989 --> 02:04.057
RESOLVED.

02:04.057 --> 02:07.094
MAY I REBUT
THAT ARGUMENT?

02:07.094 --> 02:10.298
THE FLOOR RECOGNIZES
MADAM HOOCHIE.

02:12.333 --> 02:14.802
WHILE HYBRIDS MAY BE SMALL,
THEY ARE ECONOMICAL.

02:14.802 --> 02:17.671
AND YOU CAN GET A TAX BREAK
FROM THE GOVERNMENT.

02:17.671 --> 02:19.273
AND WHEN PRESENTED
TO THE DRIVER

02:19.273 --> 02:21.041
WITH A BIG GIANT BOW
ON TOP,

02:21.041 --> 02:24.378
IT MAKES A MEMORABLE GIFT FOR
YOUR DAUGHTER'S 16th BIRTHDAY!

02:24.378 --> 02:27.715
MADAM BAT,
MAY I REBUT THAT?

02:27.715 --> 02:30.083
THE FLOOR RECOGNIZES
THE GENTLEMAN

02:30.083 --> 02:33.721
WITH THE
MONSTER-TRUCK-SIZED HEAD.

02:33.721 --> 02:36.857
HELL NO, WE'RE NOT GETTING YOU
A CAR! END OF DISCUSSION!

02:36.857 --> 02:40.294
GRANDMA, HOW OLD WERE YOU
WHEN YOUR DAD GOT YOU A CAR?

02:40.294 --> 02:41.762
[ LAUGHS ]

02:41.762 --> 02:44.965
OKAY, HOW OLD WAS DAD
WHEN YOU GOT HIM A CAR?

02:44.965 --> 02:45.899
[ LAUGHS ]

02:48.068 --> 02:49.937
OKAY, NONE OF YOU GUYS
GOT CARS,

02:49.937 --> 02:53.507
BUT AREN'T YOU SUPPOSED
TO WANT BETTER FOR YOUR KIDS?

02:53.507 --> 02:54.442
HA!

02:56.510 --> 02:58.712
ASK ME HOW MUCH I WANT
TO SPEND ON YOUR WEDDING.

02:58.712 --> 02:59.980
[ LAUGHS ]

02:59.980 --> 03:03.217
WHEN YOU'RE DONE WITH THAT FORK,
I NEED IT BACK.

03:05.853 --> 03:07.655
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

03:07.655 --> 03:10.591
WE HAVE TO FREE OURSELVES
FROM FOSSIL FUELS.

03:10.591 --> 03:12.426
SO YOU WANT
TO UNDERMINE OUR ECONOMY.

03:12.426 --> 03:14.462
WELL, IF YOU'RE SO SMART,
JASON,

03:14.462 --> 03:16.964
TELL US WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN THOSE RESOURCES ARE GONE.

03:16.964 --> 03:18.432
UH...

03:18.432 --> 03:21.869
[ LAUGHS ] WHO'S OUT OF GAS NOW,
RICH BOY?

03:23.804 --> 03:25.539
CARMEN,
YOU HAVE TO CONCEDE

03:25.539 --> 03:28.542
THAT FOSSIL FUEL IS CHEAPER
THAN ANY OTHER POWER SOURCE.

03:28.542 --> 03:30.143
CHEAP?

03:30.143 --> 03:32.112
YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT CHEAP?

03:32.112 --> 03:35.383
HOW MANY TIMES
HAS AMERICA'S TRUST

03:35.383 --> 03:38.252
BEEN VIOLATED
BY SOMEONE...

03:39.687 --> 03:41.855
JUST GOING OUT AND DRILLING
SOME CRUDE OIL

03:41.855 --> 03:46.660
THAT A BUNCH OF GUYS
HAVE ALREADY TAPPED?

03:46.660 --> 03:51.198
I WILL ADMIT THAT
SOMETIMES WE GO ABROAD

03:51.198 --> 03:55.303
TO SOLVE
OUR ENERGY NEEDS.

03:56.437 --> 03:58.806
WHEN THE WHOLE TIME,
RIGHT HERE AT HOME,

03:58.806 --> 04:03.644
WE HAD SUCH A PRECIOUS,
UNTAPPED RESOURCE.

04:04.812 --> 04:06.914
THAT WE'D DO ANYTHING
TO GET BACK.

04:06.914 --> 04:09.917
NO ONE'S TAPPING
MY COUNTRY'S RESOURCE

04:09.917 --> 04:11.585
TILL SHE GETS MARRIED.

04:13.821 --> 04:15.789
I LOVE MY COUNTRY.

04:15.789 --> 04:20.361
AND I WANT HER TO KNOW
I'M REALLY, REALLY SORRY.

04:23.364 --> 04:25.999
I WITHDRAW MY ARGUMENT.

04:25.999 --> 04:27.200
NO, I WITHDRAW MINE.

04:27.200 --> 04:29.937
OHH!

04:29.937 --> 04:32.373
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "OHH"?
HE CHEATED ON HER.

04:32.373 --> 04:34.775
WHAT KIND OF MOM
ARE YOU?

04:34.775 --> 04:37.911
HE'S A KID.
KIDS MAKE MISTAKES.

04:37.911 --> 04:40.348
SO YOU WOULD'VE FORGIVEN ME
THAT EASILY

04:40.348 --> 04:44.084
IF I HAD CHEATED ON YOU
IN HIGH SCHOOL?

04:44.084 --> 04:45.453
OH, HONEY.

04:45.453 --> 04:48.422
I KNOW HOW MANY
OPPORTUNITIES YOU HAD.

04:48.422 --> 04:50.858
THANK YOU
FOR BEING SO LOYAL.

04:52.693 --> 04:56.497
I COULD FIND SOMEONE
TONIGHT.

04:56.497 --> 04:59.199
OF COURSE YOU COULD.

04:59.199 --> 05:00.634
LET'S GO TO THE CLUB.

05:00.634 --> 05:03.504
ME AND YOU -- WE'LL BE LIKE
STARSKY AND HUTCH.

05:03.504 --> 05:05.839
I'LL THROW YOU OUT THERE
LIKE CHUM,

05:05.839 --> 05:07.808
AND THEN
I'LL FOLLOW BEHIND.

05:07.808 --> 05:10.344
[ INTRO TO WAR'S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

05:14.615 --> 05:20.454
* ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER *

05:29.997 --> 05:31.298
I COULD CHEAT ON YOU

05:31.298 --> 05:35.302
WITH THAT LADY
FROM THE POST OFFICE.

05:35.302 --> 05:36.604
UH-HUH.

05:36.604 --> 05:39.039
OR THE BIG LADY
AT THE DRY CLEANERS

05:39.039 --> 05:42.275
WHO'S ALWAYS THANKING ME
FOR BEING A MESSY EATER.

05:42.275 --> 05:43.411
MM-HMM.

05:43.411 --> 05:44.845
THE GIRL AT THE BANK.

05:44.845 --> 05:48.215
EVEN WHEN SHE'S HELPING
ANOTHER CUSTOMER,

05:48.215 --> 05:50.618
SHE CAN'T HELP
BUT CHECK ME OUT.

05:50.618 --> 05:53.654
SHE HAS A LAZY EYE,
GEORGE.

05:56.156 --> 05:57.958
MOM, DAD.

05:57.958 --> 06:00.027
YOU GOT SOME MORE FLOWERS
FROM JASON.

06:00.027 --> 06:01.862
OH, YEAH. IT'S OUR
TWO-WEEK ANNIVERSARY.

06:01.862 --> 06:03.664
HE GOT YOU FLOWERS
FOR THAT?

06:03.664 --> 06:06.266
I TOLD HIM TO. THIS TIME,
I'M CALLING THE SHOTS.

06:06.266 --> 06:07.868
HE'S GONNA HAVE TO
JUMP THROUGH HOOPS

06:07.868 --> 06:09.570
BEFORE I CAN
TRUST HIM AGAIN.

06:09.570 --> 06:11.939
WHEN HE BROKE YOUR HEART,
HE BROKE ALL OUR HEARTS.

06:11.939 --> 06:13.807
I'M GONNA STAY
EMOTIONALLY UNAVAILABLE

06:13.807 --> 06:15.075
TILL HE GETS ME
A PUTTER.

06:15.075 --> 06:16.477
GEORGE!

06:16.477 --> 06:20.848
AND SOME CREAM
FOR YOUR MOM'S ALLIGATOR ELBOWS.

06:20.848 --> 06:24.518
CAN YOU SIT DOWN? THERE'S
SOMETHING I WANT TO TALK ABOUT.

06:24.518 --> 06:26.687
OKAY, CARMEN,
WE TALKED ABOUT THIS.

06:26.687 --> 06:29.089
YOU'RE NOT
GETTING A CAR.
IT'S NOT THAT.

06:29.089 --> 06:30.924
BUT I AM TURNING 16
ON SATURDAY,

06:30.924 --> 06:32.493
AND I DO FEEL
I'M OLD ENOUGH TO --

06:32.493 --> 06:34.261
NO TATTOOS, EITHER!

06:34.261 --> 06:36.630
I WANT
BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS.

06:38.098 --> 06:42.202
WHAT ABOUT A LITTLE BUTTERFLY
ON YOUR ANKLE THAT SAYS --

06:42.202 --> 06:43.437
THAT SAYS "VIRGIN,"

06:43.437 --> 06:46.139
WITH THE WINGS CLOSED,
LIKE THAT?

06:46.139 --> 06:48.676
DAD, I'M SERIOUS.

06:48.676 --> 06:51.311
CARMEN, WE'RE NOT GETTING YOU
BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS!

06:51.311 --> 06:53.481
HAS JASON
BEEN PRESSURING YOU?

06:53.481 --> 06:54.915
NO, NO,
THIS IS MY IDEA.

06:54.915 --> 06:56.750
I WANT TO TAKE RESPONSIBILITY
FOR MY BODY.

06:56.750 --> 06:58.285
AND WHEN THE TIME COMES,

06:58.285 --> 07:01.522
CONDOMS ARE IMPORTANT,
BUT THEY'RE NOT GONNA BE ENOUGH.

07:01.522 --> 07:03.624
IT'S ONLY 98% EFFECTIVE
AGAINST PREGNANCY.

07:03.624 --> 07:05.926
I WANT TO BE SURE
THAT I'M ABSOLUTELY SAFE.

07:05.926 --> 07:10.197
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"WHEN THE DAY COMES"?

07:10.197 --> 07:14.101
WELL, LET'S TALK
ABOUT THAT TOGETHER.

07:14.101 --> 07:17.771
HOW DOES...
MARCH WORK FOR YOU?

07:20.508 --> 07:24.411
I'M NOT GONNA PICK THE DAY
MY DAUGHTER LOSES HER VIRGINITY!

07:24.411 --> 07:26.580
AND I'M SURE AS HELL
NOT GONNA DO IT

07:26.580 --> 07:29.016
ON MY NICE
GOLFING-DOGS CALENDAR!

07:29.016 --> 07:30.884
THAT'S JUST WRONG!

07:30.884 --> 07:32.753
DAD, I'M WILLING
TO COMPROMISE.

07:32.753 --> 07:35.422
YEAH, I THINK
WE ALL GET THAT. NO.

07:35.422 --> 07:37.290
OKAY, LET ME TRY
ANOTHER APPROACH.

07:37.290 --> 07:40.728
WHAT ARE THE CRITERIA I HAVE TO
MEET IN ORDER TO HAVE SEX?

07:40.728 --> 07:42.563
YOU HAVE TO BE MARRIED...

07:42.563 --> 07:44.798
OR HAVE A LETTER
FROM THE POPE.

07:47.835 --> 07:49.302
DON'T BE SUCH A HYPOCRITE.

07:49.302 --> 07:51.238
WERE YOU MARRIED
WHEN YOU LOST YOUR VIRGINITY?

07:51.238 --> 07:54.174
YOUR MOTHER WAS
THE FIRST WOMAN I WAS WITH,

07:54.174 --> 07:55.509
AND I MARRIED HER.

07:55.509 --> 07:57.845
SO YOU'VE ONLY HAD SEX
WITH ONE WOMAN?

07:57.845 --> 08:02.583
DON'T SAY IT LIKE THAT!
THAT'S HOW IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE!

08:02.583 --> 08:04.818
I'M MANY WOMEN
FOR YOUR FATHER.

08:04.818 --> 08:08.822
OH, GOD!
THAT'S WHY YOU HAVE THE WIGS!

08:13.694 --> 08:15.428
THE POINT IS,

08:15.428 --> 08:18.732
YOUR FATHER AND I WAITED
TILL WE WERE OF LEGAL AGE.

08:18.732 --> 08:20.333
ALL RIGHT,
LET'S COMPROMISE.

08:20.333 --> 08:22.335
I WON'T HAVE SEX,
BUT I'LL STILL GET THE PILLS.

08:22.335 --> 08:24.271
FOR WHAT?
THEY'RE GOOD
FOR YOUR SKIN.

08:24.271 --> 08:26.607
YOUR SKIN'S FINE.
THEY MIGHT BE GOOD
FOR YOUR HEART.

08:26.607 --> 08:28.842
YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT YOUR HEART!

08:28.842 --> 08:30.644
THEY HELP
REGULATE YOUR PERIOD.

08:30.644 --> 08:32.312
DON'T BE SO QUICK

08:32.312 --> 08:35.816
TO GIVE UP THE BEAUTY
OF AN UNEXPECTED PERIOD.

08:37.284 --> 08:40.419
SO, HOW ABOUT A NICE CASHMERE
SWEATER FOR YOUR BIRTHDAY?

08:40.419 --> 08:41.688
WHAT COLOR
DO YOU WANT?

08:41.688 --> 08:43.155
WHATEVER COLOR MATCHES

08:43.155 --> 08:45.559
THE CASHMERE SHACKLES
I WEAR IN THIS HOUSE.

08:45.559 --> 08:48.662
I KNOW WHY
THE CAGED BIRD SINGS.

08:50.463 --> 08:52.199
WELL, YOU'RE DREAMING

08:52.199 --> 08:55.769
IF YOU THINK WE'RE GETTING YOU
A SWEATER AND A BIRD.

08:55.769 --> 08:57.571
YOU KNOW WHO'S BEHIND THIS?
JASON.

08:57.571 --> 08:58.939
I HATE HIM.

09:00.440 --> 09:02.009
HE LEFT CARMEN
FOR THAT GIRL

09:02.009 --> 09:04.578
WHO HAD THE REPUTATION
FOR DOING EVERYTHING.

09:04.578 --> 09:06.146
HE'S GOT EXPERIENCE NOW.

09:06.146 --> 09:09.549
I THINK IT'S TIME
JASON AND I HAD A LITTLE TALK.

09:09.549 --> 09:11.952
YOU BETTER SCARE
SOME SENSE INTO HIM.

09:11.952 --> 09:14.788
I KNOW -- AT THAT AGE,
WHEN AN ATTRACTIVE GUY

09:14.788 --> 09:18.592
PRESSURES A GIRL TO HAVE SEX,
IT'S REALLY HARD TO SAY NO.

09:22.796 --> 09:24.965
SORRY I PRESSURED YOU,
BABY.

09:28.101 --> 09:30.037
WHAT?

09:30.037 --> 09:34.642
IN HIGH SCHOOL, I MIGHT HAVE
COME ON A LITTLE TOO STRONG.

09:34.642 --> 09:37.811
OH, YEAH.

09:37.811 --> 09:40.380
OH, THAT WAS TOUGH.

09:58.265 --> 09:59.199
COME HERE!

10:02.169 --> 10:04.204
WHAT'S UP, MR. LOPEZ?

10:04.204 --> 10:05.839
YOU KNOW, WE...

10:08.375 --> 10:10.744
...HAVEN'T HAD A GOOD TALK
IN A WHILE.

10:10.744 --> 10:13.346
OHH, I MISS OUR TALKS.

10:13.346 --> 10:15.749
SO -- HEH HEH...

10:15.749 --> 10:18.118
STILL A VIRGIN?

10:20.287 --> 10:21.789
UH, PRETTY MUCH.

10:21.789 --> 10:23.256
WHEN YOU LEFT CARMEN,

10:23.256 --> 10:26.827
YOU WENT OVER
WITH THAT CINDY LESCHIN GIRL.

10:26.827 --> 10:29.262
LOOK, I DON'T CARE, DUDE.
I'M NOT HER DAD.

10:29.262 --> 10:31.598
TELL ME ABOUT IT, STUD.
WA-CHA.

10:31.598 --> 10:34.234
[ WHISTLES ]

10:36.603 --> 10:39.372
LOOK, MR. LOPEZ,
I-I'M NEW AT THIS,

10:39.372 --> 10:42.676
BUT I'M PRETTY SURE
THIS IS NOT COOL.

10:42.676 --> 10:44.644
ARE YOU A VIRGIN
OR AREN'T YOU?!

10:44.644 --> 10:47.380
CARMEN AND I
HAVEN'T DONE ANYTHING.

10:47.380 --> 10:49.282
OH, BUT YOU WANT TO.

10:49.282 --> 10:50.851
NO.

10:50.851 --> 10:53.186
WHY NOT?!
SHE'S A BEAUTIFUL GIRL!

10:53.186 --> 10:55.388
OKAY, YES.

10:55.388 --> 10:57.224
HOW DARE YOU?!

10:57.224 --> 10:58.491
NO!

10:58.491 --> 11:00.027
YES!
I DON'T KNOW!

11:00.027 --> 11:02.062
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO SAY?

11:02.062 --> 11:05.465
I WANT YOU TO ADMIT YOU'RE
PUSHING MY DAUGHTER TO HAVE SEX.

11:05.465 --> 11:06.900
I HAVEN'T EVEN
BROUGHT IT UP.

11:06.900 --> 11:09.202
DON'T LIE TO ME.
I'M NOT. I SWEAR.

11:09.202 --> 11:12.139
THEN WHY DID SHE ASK US
FOR BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS?

11:12.139 --> 11:15.242
REALLY? SHE ASKED
FOR BIRTH CONTROL?

11:15.242 --> 11:16.443
NO WAY!

11:17.978 --> 11:22.649
NO WAY SHOULD YOU ALLOW HER
TO HAVE THOSE.

11:22.649 --> 11:24.317
SO THIS WASN'T YOUR IDEA?

11:24.317 --> 11:26.486
LOOK, MR. LOPEZ,

11:26.486 --> 11:29.222
I'M WALKING ON EGGSHELLS
WITH CARMEN AS IT IS.

11:29.222 --> 11:31.959
I WOULD NEVER DO ANYTHING
TO PRESSURE HER.

11:31.959 --> 11:34.127
I'M JUST GLAD
SHE TOOK ME BACK.

11:34.127 --> 11:36.463
DAMN!

11:36.463 --> 11:37.765
SO IT WAS HER IDEA.

11:37.765 --> 11:39.299
ALL THIS TIME,

11:39.299 --> 11:41.769
I'VE BEEN WORRYING
ABOUT BOYS PRESSURING HER.

11:41.769 --> 11:43.670
I EVEN TOLD HER
ALL THE TRICKS

11:43.670 --> 11:45.806
GUYS WOULD USE
TO GET HER INTO BED.

11:45.806 --> 11:48.141
OH, MY GOD --
I GAVE HER OUR PLAYBOOK!

11:50.610 --> 11:52.412
NO MATTER WHAT SHE SAYS,

11:52.412 --> 11:56.016
NOBODY JUST LIKES
TO LIE THERE NAKED AND HUG.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.222
[ DOOR OPENS ]

12:02.222 --> 12:04.157
HEY!

12:04.157 --> 12:07.160
I JUST GOT PAID FOR
THE HARRIS WEDDING I PLANNED,

12:07.160 --> 12:10.330
AND I'M IN THE MOOD
TO CELEBRATE.

12:10.330 --> 12:12.332
I KNOW IT'S NOT
THE SAME AS CASH,

12:12.332 --> 12:14.301
BUT WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE GET NAKED

12:14.301 --> 12:16.303
AND ROLL AROUND
ON THE CHECK?

12:16.303 --> 12:17.938
[ WHISTLES ]

12:20.974 --> 12:23.143
NOT NOW. COME ON.

12:23.143 --> 12:24.077
OH?

12:24.077 --> 12:28.148
IS SOMEBODY
PLAYING HARD TO GET?

12:28.148 --> 12:31.885
WELL, I AM NOT AFRAID
TO DRAG YOU UPSTAIRS

12:31.885 --> 12:34.955
AND HAVE MY WAY
WITH YOU, MISTER.

12:34.955 --> 12:37.657
THIS IS WHY OUR DAUGHTER'S
A SEXUAL PREDATOR!

12:37.657 --> 12:39.692
SHE GETS IT FROM YOU!

12:39.692 --> 12:41.494
WHAT?

12:41.494 --> 12:42.896
I TALKED TO JASON.

12:42.896 --> 12:45.833
CARMEN'S THE ONE
WHO WANTS TO HAVE SEX.

12:45.833 --> 12:48.035
SHE'S PRESSURING HIM?

12:48.035 --> 12:49.602
THAT'S WHAT I SAID.

12:49.602 --> 12:53.140
YOU'RE SO FULL OF LUST,
YOU CAN'T EVEN HEAR RIGHT!

12:55.308 --> 12:57.911
I DON'T FEEL GOOD.
MY STOMACH HURTS.

12:57.911 --> 12:59.546
WHAT DID YOU EAT, HONEY?

12:59.546 --> 13:02.682
WELL, I WAS IN CARMEN'S ROOM,
AND I FOUND SOME MINTS.

13:02.682 --> 13:04.451
BUT THEY
DIDN'T TASTE RIGHT.

13:04.451 --> 13:05.752
CARMEN!

13:05.752 --> 13:07.320
WHAT'S UP?

13:07.320 --> 13:09.589
YOUR BROTHER ATE YOUR MINTS,
AND HE DOESN'T FEEL GOOD.

13:09.589 --> 13:11.224
WHAT MINTS?

13:11.224 --> 13:14.361
THE ONES IN THE TIN IN YOUR
WINTER JACKET UNDER YOUR BED.

13:14.361 --> 13:15.896
OH, MY GOD.

13:17.364 --> 13:18.966
OH. HEH HEH.

13:18.966 --> 13:20.800
THOSE MINTS.

13:20.800 --> 13:23.570
THEY'RE PROBABLY
JUST STALE.

13:23.570 --> 13:26.139
SO, HOW MANY
DID YOU TAKE?

13:26.139 --> 13:29.376
I ATE FIVE --
MONDAY THROUGH FRIDAY.

13:33.380 --> 13:36.049
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"MONDAY THROUGH FRIDAY"?!

13:36.049 --> 13:38.118
THERE'S A MONTH'S WORTH
ON THIS WHEEL.

13:38.118 --> 13:40.387
YOU'RE ON THE PILL?!

13:40.387 --> 13:41.654
WELL...

13:41.654 --> 13:44.124
SO IS MAX!

13:44.124 --> 13:47.827
ANGIE,
CALL POISON CONTROL.

13:47.827 --> 13:50.063
I'M SURE EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE FINE.

13:50.063 --> 13:51.098
WHAT'S GOING ON?

13:51.098 --> 13:53.700
UH, THOSE WEREN'T MINTS,
HONEY.

13:53.700 --> 13:55.969
THEY WERE
BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS.

13:55.969 --> 13:57.871
OH, NO.
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN?

13:57.871 --> 14:00.207
YOUR SISTER'S
GONNA GET KILLED.

14:00.207 --> 14:02.242
AND IF YOU'RE ANYTHING
LIKE YOUR MOM,

14:02.242 --> 14:05.512
YOU MAY EXPERIENCE SOME
TENDERNESS AROUND YOUR BREASTS.

14:14.988 --> 14:17.157
THANK YOU.

14:17.157 --> 14:19.026
POISON CONTROL SAYS
YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE.

14:19.026 --> 14:20.793
ARE YOU HAVING SEX?

14:20.793 --> 14:22.329
NO.

14:22.329 --> 14:25.198
WHY DID YOU GO BEHIND OUR BACKS
TO GET THESE PILLS?

14:25.198 --> 14:26.934
CARMEN, WE TALKED
ABOUT THIS.

14:26.934 --> 14:28.701
NO, WE DIDN'T TALK
ABOUT ANYTHING.

14:28.701 --> 14:31.771
DAD TOLD ME WHAT TO DO,
LIKE I WAS SOME LITTLE KID.

14:31.771 --> 14:33.273
I DIDN'T HAVE
ANY SAY IN IT.

14:33.273 --> 14:35.775
YOU WANT TO HAVE A SAY?
SAY GOODBYE TO THESE.

14:35.775 --> 14:37.744
WHERE DID YOU GET
THE PILLS?

14:37.744 --> 14:39.212
WE WENT
TO THE FREE CLINIC.

14:39.212 --> 14:41.881
UNLIKE SOME PEOPLE,
THEY TREAT ME LIKE AN ADULT.

14:41.881 --> 14:43.783
"WE"?

14:43.783 --> 14:46.386
WHO WENT WITH YOU?
WAS IT JASON?

14:46.386 --> 14:49.189
IT DOESN'T MATTER.
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA FIND OUT.

14:49.189 --> 14:50.623
JUST LET IT GO.

14:50.623 --> 14:52.159
MAX...

14:52.159 --> 14:56.063
I'LL GIVE YOU $5, HOMEBOY,
IF YOU KNOW ANYTHING.

14:56.063 --> 14:57.931
I HEARD THEM TALKING.

14:57.931 --> 14:59.766
GRANDMA BENNY TOOK HER.

14:59.766 --> 15:02.970
YOU'RE NOT GETTING A DIME.
NOBODY LIKES A TATTLETALE.

15:04.437 --> 15:06.006
[ WHISTLING ]

15:07.407 --> 15:11.411
JUST CAME IN TO GET SOME SNACKS
FOR THE POKER GAME.

15:11.411 --> 15:13.013
[ HUMMING ]

15:13.013 --> 15:15.215
WE'VE ALREADY STARTED,
GEORGE.

15:19.919 --> 15:22.055
WHAT?

15:23.456 --> 15:26.393
YOU TOOK MY 16-YEAR-OLD DAUGHTER
TO GET BIRTH CONTROL?

15:27.427 --> 15:29.963
YOU DON'T HAVE TO THANK ME.

15:31.331 --> 15:35.502
JUST GIVE ME 10 BUCKS FOR GAS,
AND WE'LL BE EVEN.

15:43.910 --> 15:45.178
WE HAVE TO TALK.

15:45.178 --> 15:48.248
BEFORE YOU SAY ANYTHING,
I WANT TO OWN UP

15:48.248 --> 15:51.584
AND TAKE FULL RESPONSIBILITY
FOR DRIVING HER THERE.

15:51.584 --> 15:54.988
BUT VIC WAS THE ONE WHO TOLD HER
ABOUT THE FREE CLINIC

15:54.988 --> 15:57.857
AND SHE DIDN'T NEED PERMISSION
TO GET BIRTH CONTROL.

15:57.857 --> 15:59.426
THERE. I'VE SAID IT.

15:59.426 --> 16:02.095
LET THE CHIPS FALL
WHERE THEY MAY.

16:02.095 --> 16:04.331
TO RECAP,
IT'S VIC'S FAULT.

16:04.331 --> 16:07.967
DADDY, IS THAT TRUE?

16:07.967 --> 16:11.704
LOOK,
THIS WASN'T EASY FOR ME.

16:11.704 --> 16:14.607
AND I TOLD CARMEN THAT
I DID NOT CONDONE HER BEHAVIOR.

16:14.607 --> 16:17.110
BUT SHE SAID
SHE WAS INTENT ON DOING THIS,

16:17.110 --> 16:19.579
AND I TOLD HER
ABOUT THE FREE CLINIC.

16:19.579 --> 16:22.049
I DID WHAT ANY OTHER DOCTOR
WOULD DO.

16:22.049 --> 16:24.317
OF COURSE,
IT'S JUST INFORMATION.

16:24.317 --> 16:27.620
IT MEANS NOTHING UNLESS
SOMEBODY DRIVES HER THERE!

16:29.756 --> 16:31.158
YOU'RE GRANDPARENTS.

16:31.158 --> 16:33.393
YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO TELL HER WHAT IT WAS LIKE

16:33.393 --> 16:35.928
WHEN BREAD WAS A NICKEL,
NOT PIMP THEM OUT!

16:35.928 --> 16:38.065
I STAND BY MY DECISION.

16:38.065 --> 16:39.466
YEAH?

16:39.466 --> 16:41.868
DID YOU GIVE ANGIE THE PILL
WHEN SHE WAS 16?

16:41.868 --> 16:43.136
ABSOLUTELY NOT!

16:43.136 --> 16:45.838
I GAVE IT
TO HER SISTER GLORIA.

16:45.838 --> 16:48.808
WHAT?! HOW COULD YOU GIVE IT
TO HER AND NOT ME?

16:48.808 --> 16:51.611
BECAUSE WHEN I SAID
THAT SEX WAS A SACRED BOND

16:51.611 --> 16:54.681
THAT SHOULD ONLY OCCUR BETWEEN
A MARRIED MAN AND HIS WIFE,

16:54.681 --> 16:56.015
YOU BELIEVED ME.

16:56.015 --> 16:57.584
SHE DIDN'T.

16:59.652 --> 17:02.655
LET'S GET REAL HERE.
I GOT KNOCKED UP WHEN I WAS 16.

17:02.655 --> 17:04.723
DO YOU WANT THAT
TO HAPPEN TO CARMEN?

17:04.723 --> 17:08.461
I JUST WANT EVERYONE TO KNOW
THAT I HAVE NOT HAD SEX YET.

17:08.461 --> 17:12.165
AND WHEN THAT DAY COMES,
YOU WILL ALL GET AN E-MAIL.

17:12.165 --> 17:15.902
OKAY, HERE'S THE DEAL.

17:15.902 --> 17:17.237
THEY ARE OUR CHILDREN.

17:17.237 --> 17:19.872
WE WILL RAISE THEM
OUR WAY.

17:19.872 --> 17:22.909
STAY OUT OF IT OR YOU WON'T BE
ALLOWED IN THIS HOUSE.

17:22.909 --> 17:24.243
POKER GAME'S OVER.

17:24.243 --> 17:26.713
BUT I-I HAVE FOUR ACES!

17:26.713 --> 17:28.013
FOLD.
FOLD.

17:28.013 --> 17:29.149
AWW!

17:31.418 --> 17:34.287
OKAY,
SHE'S TURNING 16 FRIDAY.

17:34.287 --> 17:37.190
SHE'S ALREADY STARTED
TAKING BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS.

17:37.190 --> 17:39.826
WE GOT TO DO SOMETHING --
FAST.

17:39.826 --> 17:41.228
[ SODA CAN OPENS ]

17:41.228 --> 17:42.895
I'M NOT TALKING TO YOU.

17:42.895 --> 17:44.664
FINE.
DON'T TALK TO ME.

17:44.664 --> 17:48.067
BUT THIS IS SOMETHING
I KNOW ABOUT AND YOU DON'T.

17:48.067 --> 17:49.702
YOU'VE HELPED ENOUGH,
BENNY.

17:49.702 --> 17:52.272
I DIDN'T WANT TO SAY THIS
IN FRONT OF CARMEN,

17:52.272 --> 17:53.740
BUT YOU CAN'T STOP HER.

17:53.740 --> 17:55.742
MY DAD SAID
HE WOULD KILL ME.

17:55.742 --> 17:59.112
AND I BELIEVED HIM,
AND I STILL WENT OUT AND DID IT.

17:59.112 --> 18:00.313
CARMEN'S NOT YOU.

18:00.313 --> 18:02.449
SHE'S NOT WILLING
TO DO ANYTHING

18:02.449 --> 18:05.084
FOR A CHEESEBURGER
AND A RIDE HOME.

18:10.323 --> 18:13.726
IT WAS RAINING,
AND IT WAS CHICKEN NUGGETS.

18:15.795 --> 18:17.630
THIS IS HOW RUMORS START.

18:17.630 --> 18:19.632
WE'RE GONNA FIND A WAY
TO STOP CARMEN.

18:19.632 --> 18:20.767
[ SCOFFS ] NO.

18:20.767 --> 18:23.503
THIS IS GONNA HAPPEN
ONE OF TWO WAYS --

18:23.503 --> 18:26.873
PLANNED AND PROTECTED
OR HOT AND SPONTANEOUS.

18:26.873 --> 18:28.007
MOM!

18:28.007 --> 18:29.509
BOTH HAVE THEIR ADVANTAGES.

18:29.509 --> 18:31.644
ONE WAY,
YOU DON'T GET PREGNANT.

18:31.644 --> 18:33.045
THE OTHER WAY...

18:33.045 --> 18:35.215
WOW.

18:40.520 --> 18:43.823
DOES YOUR MOM
ALWAYS HAVE TO BE SO BLUNT?

18:43.823 --> 18:47.794
LOOK, I DIDN'T WANT TO SAY THIS
IN FRONT OF CARMEN,

18:47.794 --> 18:51.831
BUT THIS IS GOING TO HAPPEN
ONE OF TWO WAYS --

18:51.831 --> 18:53.533
SMART AND WITH PROTECTION

18:53.533 --> 18:56.403
OR IN A FIELD OF TOBACCO
UNDER A CUBAN MOON

18:56.403 --> 18:59.872
WITH THE GODFATHER OF REVOLUTION
IN THE BACKGROUND.

18:59.872 --> 19:02.209
WOW.

19:08.381 --> 19:11.651
I HATE TO SAY IT,
BUT THEY'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.

19:11.651 --> 19:13.386
DON'T BACK DOWN.
WE'RE STOPPING CARMEN.

19:13.386 --> 19:14.821
WE HAVE TO.

19:14.821 --> 19:16.856
SHE'S NOT READY
FOR THE EMOTIONAL CONSEQUENCES

19:16.856 --> 19:18.925
THAT GO ALONG
WITH A SEXUAL RELATIONSHIP.

19:18.925 --> 19:21.528
AND WE ARE NOT EMOTIONALLY
PREPARED TO DEAL WITH

19:21.528 --> 19:24.397
OUR DAUGHTER CROSSING
THE THRESHOLD INTO WOMANHOOD.

19:26.366 --> 19:28.368
THAT'S IT!
WHAT?

19:28.368 --> 19:30.136
IF YOU CAN TEACH CARMEN
TO BORE A GUY

19:30.136 --> 19:33.172
LIKE YOU JUST BORED ME,
NOBODY'LL WANT TO BE WITH HER.

19:38.177 --> 19:39.812
WELL,
I'M NOT SURPRISED

19:39.812 --> 19:41.948
THERE'S NOTHING DOWN HERE
FOR MY BIRTHDAY.

19:41.948 --> 19:44.217
I KNOW YOU GUYS
ARE STILL MAD AT ME.

19:44.217 --> 19:46.719
MNH-MNH.
WE'RE NOT MAD.

19:46.719 --> 19:49.322
WE TALKED LAST NIGHT.
WE REALIZED YOU'RE 16.

19:49.322 --> 19:51.491
WE CAN'T STOP YOU
FROM GROWING UP.

19:51.491 --> 19:54.561
SO, WE HAVE
A BIRTHDAY SURPRISE FOR YOU.

19:54.561 --> 19:55.962
WHAT?

19:57.364 --> 19:59.999
NO, WAIT.
W-WHERE ARE WE GOING?

19:59.999 --> 20:02.669
TO A MEXICAN CONVENT.

20:07.039 --> 20:08.341
HAPPY BIRTHDAY!

20:08.341 --> 20:11.578
OH, MY GOD!
YOU GUYS GOT ME A CAR?!

20:11.578 --> 20:13.613
I LOVE YOU!
YOU GUYS ARE THE BEST!

20:13.613 --> 20:16.182
THERE'S JUST ONE CATCH --
YOU CAN ONLY KEEP THE CAR

20:16.182 --> 20:18.184
IF YOU STAY A VIRGIN
TILL YOU'RE 40.

20:18.184 --> 20:20.152
GEORGE!

20:20.152 --> 20:21.354
18.

20:21.354 --> 20:23.222
YOU GUYS ARE BRIBING ME?

20:23.222 --> 20:25.091
YEP. IT'S UP TO YOU.

20:25.091 --> 20:28.227
THE CAR...

20:28.227 --> 20:29.996
OR SEX.

20:29.996 --> 20:31.898
ARE YOU KIDDING?
THE CAR!

20:33.433 --> 20:36.969
I HEAR IT'S NOT THAT GREAT
THE FIRST COUPLE OF TIMES.

20:36.969 --> 20:38.771
HOW CAN IT BE
WITH ALL THAT

20:38.771 --> 20:43.610
"WHAT ARE YOU THINKING ABOUT
NOW? HOW ABOUT NOW? NOW?"

20:45.412 --> 20:46.713
WHAT'S GOING ON?

20:46.713 --> 20:48.781
JUST SHOWING CARMEN
HER BIRTHDAY SURPRISE.

20:48.781 --> 20:49.816
THEY GOT ME A CAR!

20:49.816 --> 20:51.718
OH, THAT IS
AN AWESOME SURPRISE.

20:51.718 --> 20:54.854
THERE'S A SURPRISE FOR YOU, TOO,
FOOL. TELL HIM.

20:54.854 --> 20:56.456
THEY GAVE ME A CHOICE --

20:56.456 --> 20:58.525
I CAN EITHER HAVE
THE CAR...

20:58.525 --> 21:00.159
OR SEX BEFORE I'M 18.

21:00.159 --> 21:01.928
GUESS WHAT I PICKED.

21:01.928 --> 21:03.930
[ HORN HONKS ]

21:03.930 --> 21:05.465
OH.

21:05.465 --> 21:07.900
WELL, I ALREADY
HAVE A CAR, BUT...

21:07.900 --> 21:09.702
YOU KNOW, THAT'S COOL.

21:09.702 --> 21:10.837
YEAH.

21:12.339 --> 21:14.774
JASON, WHY DON'T YOU
TAKE CARMEN OUT

21:14.774 --> 21:16.776
FOR A NICE
BIRTHDAY DINNER.

21:16.776 --> 21:19.679
AND YOU KNOW WHAT, MY MAN?
NO CURFEW.

21:19.679 --> 21:20.547
[ SNIFFS ]
YOU'LL BE HOME EARLY.
